children: We can select a single entry using its ID:

mimes.text/html: RegistryEntry( name = "antiquewhite" (String) color = ██ RGB{N0f8}(0.98,0.922,0.843) (ColorTypes.Color) )

children: And get a summary of fields in the registry:

mimes.text/html: Fields in registry "Colors" Name Column Type Description Name :name (ID) String The name of the color Color :color ColorTypes.Color The color value
